Description:
	The model generator creates a migration witch adding destroyed column to the specified model(s).

Example:
	./script/generate nodestroyed ALL

	This will create an Migration:
	Migration:  db/migrate/XXX_add_destroyed_field_to_all_needed_models.rb


	./script/generate nodestroyed users,posts
	the users and posts are table names.
	
	This will create an Migration:
	Migration:  db/migrate/XXX_add_destroyed_field_to_users_posts.rb

